clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For the treatment of bacterial infection

contraindications.disease: Troleandomycin inhibits clearance of theophylline and can increase the likelyhood of toxicity in patients recieving theophylline therapy A19571
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Troleandomycin like other macrolide antibiotics inhibits bacterial protein synthesis to prevent growth
